{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"beb15b808b","title":"提高警惕，切勿上当","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"601dbb5714","index":0,"year":1946,"month":8,"day":24,"articleId":"beb15b808b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"eeaa97c19b","type":"paragraph","text":"提高警惕，切勿上当口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"beb15b808b"},{"id":"663e5c6cfb","type":"paragraph","text":"1946年8月24日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"beb15b808b"},{"id":"be3bfac7cf","type":"paragraph","text":"最近三个月，国、美密课诱致林彪、陈毅、李先念、贺龙诸重要负责人去大城市谈判，企图留他们，以利进攻，但为我识破拒绝。最近国、美密谋在进攻热河之前诱致李运昌，现已拒绝。蒋军攻热得手后，将攻哈尔滨，彼时可能又发生诱骗企图，望东北局及李、伍、边先有精神准备，切勿上当。八个月来我们受国、美密课欺骗之事极多极大，应当提高警场性[I]这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的致东北局、热河分局以及李立三、任修权、边章伍、周恩来、叶剑英电的主要内容。边章伍，当时任北平军事调","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"beb15b808b"}],"page":{"id":"52620a3fdb","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"beb15b808b","start":94,"end":94}}}},"__N_SSG":true}